    "content": "1. 상미분제차차방정식 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026y''+ay'+by=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026D^2+aD+b=0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ 2. 서로 다른, 실수 해 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha,\\beta \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1e^{\\alpha x}+c_2e^{\\beta x}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$y''-y'-2y'=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left(D-2\\right)\\left(D+1\\right)=0\\rightarrow D=-1,2 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1e^{-1x}+c_2e^{2x}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$y''-4y'=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D\\left(D-4\\right)=0\\rightarrow D=0,4 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1+c_2e^{4x}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r2. 중근 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=\\left(c_1+c_2x\\right)e^{\\alpha x}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$y''+6y'+9y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left(D+3\\right)^2=0 \\rightarrow D=-3 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=\\left(c_1+c_2x\\right)e^{-3x}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r3. 서로 다른, 복소수 해 $$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D=\\alpha\\pm i\\beta \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=e^{\\alpha x}\\left(c_1\\cos\\beta x+c_2\\sin\\beta x\\right) \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=e^{\\alpha x}\\left(c_1e^{+i\\beta x}+c_2e^{-i\\beta x}\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ example1)\n$$y''+4y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2+4=0\\rightarrow D=\\pm 2i \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1\\cos 2x+c_2\\sin 2x\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$y''+2y'+2y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2+2D+2=0\\rightarrow D=-1\\pm \\sqrt{1-2}=-1\\pm i \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=e^{-x}\\left(c_1\\cos x+c_2\\sin x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample3)\n$$y''-2y'+10y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^2-2D+10=0\\rightarrow D=1\\pm \\sqrt{1-10}=-1\\pm 3i \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=e^{x}\\left(c_1\\cos 3x+c_2\\sin 3x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample4)\n$$y'''-2y''+3y'-6y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^3-2D^2+4D-6=0\\rightarrow \\left(D-2\\right)\\left(D^2+3\\right)=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=c_1e^{2x}+c_2\\cos 3x+c_3\\sin 3x\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample5)\n$$y'''-6y''+12y'-8y=0$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026D^3-6D^2+12D-8=0\\rightarrow \\left(D-2\\right)^3=0 \\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026y=e^{2x}\\left(c_1+c_2x+c_3 x^2\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$",
