    "content": "$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2u}{\\partial x^2}=\\frac{1}{D}\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial t}\r$$periodic boundary condition\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026u\\left(0,t\\right)=u\\left(L,t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}\\left(0,t\\right)=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}u\\left(L,t\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$해는 다음과 같다.\n$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=a_0+\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}\\left(a_{n}\\cos k_{n}x+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}x\\right)e_{}^{-Dk_{n}^2t}\r$$또는\n$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}c_{n}e_{}^{-\\left(Dk_{n}^2t-ik_{n}x\\right)}\r$$ proof1)\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=-k_{n}^2X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r$$(1) k$_{n}$≠0\n$$\rX_{n}\\left(x\\right)=a_{n}\\cos k_{n}x+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}x\r$$(2) k$_{0}$=0\n$$\rX_{n}\\left(x\\right)=a_{n}+b_{n}x\r$$boundary condition 을 적용한다.\n(1) $k_{n}\\ne0$\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(0\\right)=a_{n}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(L\\right)=a_{n}\\cos k_{n}L+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}L\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026k_{n}=\\frac{2n\\pi}{L}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$(2) k$_{0}$=0\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026b_0=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_0\\left(x\\right)=a_0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$연산자가 self-adjoint 함을 이용하여 각 계수를 구한다.\n(1) $k_{n}≠0$\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u00261=\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\left|X\\left(x\\right)\\right|^2\\right\\rbrack\r\\\\\r\u0026=\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack a_{n}^2\\cos^2k_{n}x+b_{n}^2\\sin^2k_{n}L+2a_{n}b_{n}\\cos k_{n}x\\sin k_{n}x\\right\\rbrack\r\\\\\r\u0026=\\frac{L}{2}\\left(a_{n}^2+b_{n}^2\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$(2) $k_{0}=0$\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u00261=\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\left|X_0\\left(x\\right)\\right|^2\\right\\rbrack=a_0^2L\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026a_0=\\pm\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{L}}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$시간에 대해 구하면,\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026k_{n}^2T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=\\frac{1}{D}\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left(\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}+Dk_{n}^2\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=e^{-Dk_{n}^2t}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$eigen-expansion 을 수행하면, 다음과 같다.\n$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=a_0+\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}\\left(a_{n}\\cos k_{n}x+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}x\\right)e^{-Dk_{n}^2t}\r$$만약, 초기 조건이 주어진다면, 각 계수를 구할 수 있다.\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026a_0=\\frac{1}{L}\\langle1,u\\left(x,0\\right)\\rangle\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026a_{n}=\\frac{2}{L}\\langle\\cos k_{n}x,u\\left(x,0\\right)\\rangle\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026b_{n}=\\frac{2}{L}\\langle\\sin k_{n}x,u\\left(x,0\\right)\\rangle\r\\end{aligned}\r$$ proof2)\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=-k_{n}^2X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r$$(1) k$_{n}$≠0\n$$\rX_{n}\\left(x\\right)=a_{n}e_{}^{-ik_{n}x}+b_{n}e_{}^{+ik_{n}x}\r$$(2) k$_{0}$=0\n$$\rX_0\\left(x\\right)=a_0+b_0x\r$$boundary condition 을 적용한다.\n(1) $k_{n}≠0$\n주기적 boundary condition 이므로, 아래와 같이 볼 수 있다.\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(x\\right)=b_{n}e^{+ik_{n}x}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026b_{n}=b_{n}e^{+ik_{n}L}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026k_{n}=\\frac{2n\\pi}{L}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$(2) k$_{0}$=0\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026b_0=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_0\\left(x\\right)=a_0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$따라서, x에 대한 변수분리 해는 다음과 같다.\n$$\rX_{n}\\left(x\\right)=b_{n}e_{}^{+i_{}k_{n}x}\r$$연산자가 self-adjoint 함을 이용하여 계수를 구한다.\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u00261=\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\left|X_{n}\\left(x\\right)\\right|^2\\right\\rbrack=b_{n}^2L\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026b_{n}=\\pm\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{L}}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$시간에 대해 구하면,\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026k_{n}^2T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=\\frac{1}{D}\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left(\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}+Dk_{n}^2\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=e_{}^{-Dk_{n}^2t}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$eigen-expansion 을 수행하면, 다음과 같다.\n$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}c_{n}e_{}^{-\\left(Dk_{n}^2t-ik_{n}x\\right)}\r$$만약, 초기 조건이 주어진다면, 계수를 구할 수 있다.\n$$\rc_{n}=\\frac{1}{L}\\langle e_{}^{ik_{n}x},u\\left(x,0\\right)\\rangle\r$$ Separation of Variables III: Periodic Boundaries - Partial Differential Equations | Lecture 8",
    "description": "$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2u}{\\partial x^2}=\\frac{1}{D}\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial t}\r$$periodic boundary condition\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026u\\left(0,t\\right)=u\\left(L,t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}\\left(0,t\\right)=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}u\\left(L,t\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$해는 다음과 같다.\n$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=a_0+\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}\\left(a_{n}\\cos k_{n}x+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}x\\right)e_{}^{-Dk_{n}^2t}\r$$또는\n$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}c_{n}e_{}^{-\\left(Dk_{n}^2t-ik_{n}x\\right)}\r$$ proof1)\n$$\r\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=-k_{n}^2X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r$$(1) k$_{n}$≠0\n$$\rX_{n}\\left(x\\right)=a_{n}\\cos k_{n}x+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}x\r$$(2) k$_{0}$=0\n$$\rX_{n}\\left(x\\right)=a_{n}+b_{n}x\r$$boundary condition 을 적용한다.\n(1) $k_{n}\\ne0$\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(0\\right)=a_{n}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(L\\right)=a_{n}\\cos k_{n}L+b_{n}\\sin k_{n}L\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026k_{n}=\\frac{2n\\pi}{L}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$(2) k$_{0}$=0\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026b_0=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_0\\left(x\\right)=a_0\r\\end{aligned}\r$$연산자가 self-adjoint 함을 이용하여 각 계수를 구한다.",
