    "content": "example1) wave equation\nThe vertical displacement u(x,t) of a string of length L that is freely vibrating in the vertical plane.\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}u\\left(x,t\\right)=\\frac{1}{v^2}\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial t^2}u\\left(x,t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left\\lbrack \\text{B.C}\\right\\rbrack\\quad u\\left(0,t\\right)=u\\left(L,t\\right)=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left\\lbrack \\text{I.C}\\right\\rbrack\\quad u\\left(x,0\\right)=f\\left(x\\right),\\quad u_{t}\\left(x,0\\right)=g\\left(x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026u_{n}\\left(x,t\\right)=X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\nabla^2u_{n}\\left(x,t\\right)=-k_{n}^2u_{n}\\left(x,t\\right)\\implies\\nabla^2X_{n}\\left(x\\right)=-k_{n}^2X_{n}\\left(x\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left(\\nabla^2+k_{n}^2\\right)X_{n}\\left(x\\right)=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(x\\right)=a_{x,n}\\cos k_{n}x+b_{x,n}\\sin k_{n}x\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rB.C을 적용한다.\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(0\\right)=0=a_{x,n}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(L\\right)=0=b_{x,n}\\sin k_{n}x\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r따라서,\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026k_{n}L=n\\pi,\\quad n=1,2,3,\\cdots\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026k_{n}=\\frac{n\\pi}{L},\\quad n=1,2,3,\\cdots\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026X_{n}\\left(x\\right)=b_{x,n}\\sin\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x,\\quad n=1,2,3,\\cdots\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial t^2}T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=-\\omega_{n}^2T_{n}\\left(t\\right),\\quad\\omega_{n}^2=v^2k_{n}^2\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026T_{n}\\left(t\\right)=a_{t,n}\\cos\\omega_{n}t+b_{t,n}\\sin\\omega_{n}t\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r따라서,\r$$\ru_{n}\\left(x,t\\right)=\\left(A_{n}\\cos\\omega_{n}t+B_{n}\\sin\\omega_{n}t\\right)\\sin\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\r$$\reigen-expansion 을 수행한다.\r$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=\\sum\\left(c_{n,1}\\cos\\omega_{n}t+c_{n,2}\\sin\\omega_{n}t\\right)\\sin\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\r$$\r[I.C] $u\\left(x,0\\right)=f\\left(x\\right)$\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026u\\left(x,0\\right)=\\sum c_{n,1}\\sin\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)=f\\left(x\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026c_{n,1}\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\sin^2\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack f\\left(x\\right)\\sin^{}\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\sin^2\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=\\frac12\\int_{-L}^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\sin^2\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=\\frac{L}{2}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026c_{n,1}=\\frac{2}{L}\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack f\\left(x\\right)\\sin^{}\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r[I.C] $u_{t}\\left(x,0\\right)=g\\left(x\\right)$\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026u_{t}\\left(x,0\\right)=\\sum c_{n,2}\\omega_{n}\\sin\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026c_{n,2}\\omega_{n}\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack\\sin^2\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack=\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack g\\left(x\\right)\\sin^{}\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026c_{n,2}=\\frac{2}{\\omega_{n}L}\\int_0^{L}dx\\left\\lbrack g\\left(x\\right)\\sin^{}\\left(\\frac{n\\pi}{L}x\\right)\\right\\rbrack\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rexample2)\n$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026f\\left(x\\right)\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}u+g\\left(x\\right)\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}u+h\\left(x\\right)u=\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}u+k\\left(t\\right)u\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026u\\left(a,t\\right)=u\\left(b,t\\right)=0\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026u\\left(x,0\\right)=s\\left(x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rsol\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026u_{n}\\left(x,t\\right)=X_{n}\\left(x\\right)T_{n}\\left(t\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left\\lbrack f\\left(x\\right)\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}+g\\left(x\\right)\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}+h\\left(x\\right)\\right\\rbrack X_{n}=\\lambda_{n}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rStrum-Liouville 형태로 변형한다.\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\left\\lbrack\\frac{\\partial^2}{\\partial x^2}+\\frac{g\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}+\\frac{h\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}\\right\\rbrack X_{n}=\\lambda_{n}^{}\\frac{1}{f\\left(x\\right)}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026r\\left(x\\right)=e^{\\int dx\\left\\lbrack\\frac{g\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}\\right\\rbrack}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\left\\lbrack D\\left(r\\left(x\\right)D\\right)_{}+r\\left(x\\right)\\frac{h\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}\\right\\rbrack X_{n}=\\lambda_{n}\\frac{r\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}X_{n}\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\r아래와 같은 weight function 을 선택한다.\r$$\rw\\left(x\\right)=-\\frac{r\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}=-\\frac{1}{f\\left(x\\right)}e^{\\int dx\\left\\lbrack\\frac{g\\left(x\\right)}{f\\left(x\\right)}\\right\\rbrack}\r$$\rB.C 을 만족해야 한다.\r$$X_{n}\\left(a\\right)=X_{n}\\left(b\\right)=0$$\r$$\r\\begin{aligned}\r\u0026\\lambda_{n}T_{n}=\\left\\lbrack\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial t}+k\\left(t\\right)\\right\\rbrack T_{n}\\implies\\lambda_{n}-k\\left(t\\right)=\\frac{1}{T_{n}}\\frac{\\partial T_{n}}{\\partial t}\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026\\int_0^{t}dt'\\left\\lbrack\\lambda_{n}-k\\left(t'\\right)\\right\\rbrack=\\int_0^{T_{n}}dT_{n}'\\left\\lbrack\\frac{1}{T_{n}'}\\right\\rbrack\\implies\\ln T_{n}=\\lambda_{n}t-\\int_0^{t}dt'\\left\\lbrack k\\left(t'\\right)\\right\\rbrack\r\\\\\r\\\\\r\u0026T_{n}=\\exp\\left(\\lambda_{n}t-\\int_0^{t}dt'\\left\\lbrack k\\left(t'\\right)\\right\\rbrack\\right)\r\\end{aligned}\r$$\rI.C 을 만족해야한다.\r$$T_{n}\\left(s\\right)=0$$\reigen-expansion 을 수행한다.\r$$\ru\\left(x,t\\right)=\\sum c_{n}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)\\exp\\left(\\lambda_{n}t-\\int_0^{t}dt'\\left\\lbrack k\\left(t'\\right)\\right\\rbrack\\right)\r$$\rI.C 을 만족해야 한다.\r$$u\\left(x,0\\right)=\\sum c_{n}X_{n}\\left(x\\right)=s\\left(x\\right)$$\r$X_{n}$ 은 self-adjoint 한 연산자의 eigen-vector 이므로,\r$$c_{n}=\\left\\langle X_{n}\\left(x\\right)|s\\left(x\\right)\\right\\rangle_{w}$$\rSturm–Liouville theory - Wikipedia\nSeparable partial differential equation - Wikipedia",
